tions with 5 specialized healthcare services.</p>\n </div>\n </div>\n </section>\n\n <!-- Service Areas by Service Type -->\n <section class=\"section\" style=\"background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f8fafc 0%, #ffffff 100%);\">\n <div class=\"container\">\n <!-- Stats Bar -->\n <div class=\"stats-bar\">\n <div class=\"stats-bar__item\">\n <span class=\"stats-bar__number\">296</span>\n <span class=\"stats-bar__label\">Cities Served</span>\n </div>\n <div class=\"stats-bar__item\">\n <span class=\"stats-bar__number\">21+</span>\n <span class=\"stats-bar__label\">Years Experience</span>\n </div>\n <div class=\"stats-bar__item\">\n <span class=\"stats-bar__number\">5</span>\n <span class=\"stats-bar__label\">Services Offered</span>\n </div>\n <div class=\"stats-bar__item\">\n <span class=\"stats-bar__number\">$2M</span>\n <span class=\"stats-bar__label\">Insurance Coverage</span>\n </div>\n </div>\n\n <!-- Introduction -->\n <div class=\"service-areas-intro\">\n <h2 style=\"font-size: 1.75rem; color: #1a1a2e; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\">Your Trusted Massachusetts Healthcare Partner</h2>\n <p>For over 22 years, Dory's Cleaning Services has been the trusted choice for medical offices, clinics, and healthcare facilities throughout Central and Eastern Massachusetts. From Worcester to the MetroWest area, from Newton to Framingham, we've built our reputation on precision sanitation, infection control protocols, and genuine commitment to patient and staff safety.</p>\n\n <p style=\"margin-top: 1rem;\">Our service area spans more than 100 communities across Middlesex, Worcester, and Norfolk counties. Whether you manage a medical office in Wellesley, oversee an assisted living facility in Marlborough, or direct operations at a clinic in Cambridge, we have the environment-specific expertise and flexibility to meet your sanitation needs.</p>\n\n <p style=\"margin-top: 1rem;\">What sets us apart is our commitment to using EPA-registered hospital-grade disinfectants and following CDC/OSHA guidelines for healthcare facility cleaning services. Every member of our team is fully insured (up to $2 million in coverage), background-checked, and trained in infection control protocols that ensure consistent, compliant results every time.</p>\n\n <h3 style=\"font-size: 1.25rem; color: #1a1a2e; margin: 2rem 0 1rem;\">Our Service Coverage Areas</h3>\n <p>We proudly serve the Greater Boston area, the MetroWest corridor, and communities throughout Worcester County. Our most popular service areas include:</p>\n <ul style=\"text-align: left; max-width: 600px; margin: 1rem auto; list-style: none; padding: 0;\">\n <li style=\"padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\"><strong>MetroWest:</strong> Framingham, Natick, Wellesley, Newton, Marlborough, Hudson, Sudbury</li>\n <li style=\"padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\"><strong>Worcester Area:</strong> Worcester, Shrewsbury, Westborough, Northborough, Grafton</li>\n <li style=\"padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\"><strong>Greater Boston:</strong> Cambridge, Brookline, Arlington, Lexington, Waltham</li>\n <li style=\"padding: 0.5rem 0;\"><strong>495 Corridor:</strong> Hopkinton, Milford, Franklin, Holliston, Ashland</li>\n </ul>\n\n <p style=\"margin-top: 1rem;\">Select a service below to find professional cleaning in your city. Each location page includes local pricing, availability, customer testimonials from your neighbors, and a simple online quote request form. We offer Cleaning Assessment for all new customers, and most homes can be scheduled within 48 hours.</p>\n </div>\n\n <!-- Specialty Clinics Block -->\n <div class=\"service-block\">\n <div class=\"service-block__header\">\n <div class=\"service-block__icon\">\n <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z\"/></svg>\n </div>\n <h2 class=\"service-block__title\">Specialty Clinics</h2>\n </div>\n <p clas